      "date": "2011-08-15 10:34:44.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/66951ce8-c728-11e0-a7e2-52540025f9af).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
